properties.text:
[color=#00FF00]Objective:[/color] Deliver all packages to the mailboxes

Build the conveyors by dragging them to a wooden or obsidian base.
- Wooden bases can float on water, but burn on fire.
- Obsidian bases can float on lava, but sinks on water.

Conveyors can be rotated while on the floor by [color=#FFFF00]Right Clicking[/color] them.

Press [color=#FFFF00]Enter[/color] to go to the next page...

To place the built conveyors inside the facility, put them on top of the pre-existing conveyors on the striped floor.

When a desired configuration of conveyors has been achieved, press [color=#ffff00]Enter[/color] to spawn a package on each one of the conveyors on the striped floor.

- Pressing [color=#FFFF00]Bksp[/color] at any point restarts the game.
- Use the [color=#ffff00]Mouse Scroll[/color] to rotate the camera.

Press [color=#FFFF00]Enter[/color] to start...
